Rockaway Parkway, south from Newport Street and New Lots Road, showing from left to right in the background, the homes of Williaa F.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, a view along New ots Road, from the opposite directiou, which will be Rockaway Parkway; at this point in the future.

The same, a close up of the Derick Remsen house.
